data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
This test utility shows:
- Connectivity status. This uses events and timers to show how these methods can detect USB changes
- Read ADC values – select the 'Read' button
- Read initialisation status of the LEDs and sets state of LEDs attached to b.5 and b.4 - the check boxes
- Use of LibK/WinUSB library to call the GCB USB stack
- Polls the microcontroller every 10 secs after the last USB transmission
- Recovery from USB physical D- and D+ errors by using a state engine.
... this is the example code documentation for this application and the Great Cow BASIC solution.
Enjoy
